subjectkey: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
interview_date: Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
interview_age: Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
eventname: The event name for which the data was collected

tfmri_mid_beh_switchflag: Whether the button box responses were switched
tfmri_mid_beh_performflag: Whether the participant had an acceptable performance in the task; all trial types must yield more than 3 events for both positive and negative feedback
tfmri_mid_beh_nruns: Number of valid runs in the file
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_t_nt: Total number of trials for run 1
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_t_nt: Total number of trials for run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srw_nt: Total number of small reward trials for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srw_mrt: Average reaction time for small reward trials for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srw_stdrt: Standard deviation of average reaction time for small reward trials for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srw_nt: Total number of small reward trials shown for run 1
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srw_mrt: Average reaction time for small reward trials for run 1
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srw_stdrt: Standard deviation of average reaction time for small reward trials for run 1
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srw_nt: Total number of small reward trials shown for run 2
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srw_mrt: Average reaction time for small reward trials for run 2
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srw_stdrt: Standard deviation of average reaction time for small reward trials for run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srwpfb_nt: Total number of small reward trials answered correctly for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srwpfb_rate: Number of small reward trials that yielded positive feedback in run 1 divided by the total number of small reward trials
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srwpfb_mrt: Average reaction time for small reward trials with positive feedback run 1
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srwpfb_stdrt: Standard deviation of average reaction time for small reward with positive feedback run 1
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srwpfb_nt: Total number of small reward trials answered correctly for run 2
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srwpfb_rate: Number of small reward trials that yielded positive feedback in run 2 divided by the total number of small reward trials
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srwpfb_mrt: Average reaction time for small reward trials with positive feedback run 2
tfmri_mid_r2_beh_srwpfb_stdrt: Standard deviation of average reaction time for small reward with positive feedback run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srwnfb_nt: Total number of small reward trials answered incorrectly for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srwnfb_rate: Number of small reward trials that yielded negative feedback in run 1 and run 2 combined divided by the total number of small reward trials
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srwnfb_mrt: Average reaction time for small reward trials with negative feedback for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_all_beh_srwnfb_stdrt: Standard deviation of average reaction time for small reward with negative feedback for run 1 and run 2
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srwnfb_nt: Total number of small reward trials answered incorrectly for run 1
tfmri_mid_r1_beh_srwnfb_rate: Number of small reward trials that yielded negative feedback in run 1 divided by the total number of small reward trials
